question: How many workers are working in companies 'Toolbox Creative' and 'Search Engine People' combined?
cypher:

    OPTIONAL MATCH (p:Person)-[:WORKS_IN]->(c)

MATCH (d:Company {name: 'Search Engine People'})
    OPTIONAL MATCH (p1:Person)-[:WORKS_IN]->(d)

RETURN count(p) + count(p1) as combinedCount

question: What is the highest degree earned by workers at Search Engine People? List first 3 workers who have the highest degree

question: List top 5 companies where workers who live in the United States work
cypher: MATCH (c:Country {name: 'United States'})<-[:LIVES_IN]-(p:Person)-[:WORKS_IN]->(com:Company) RETURN com.name as Company, COUNT(DISTINCT p) as worker ORDER BY worker DESC LIMIT 5

question: What are the names of the industry where workers who speak Czech work? List first 3 industry names

question: Find top 3 countries where people in the real estate industry live
cypher:
MATCH (c:Company)-[:IS_IN]->(:Industry {name: 'Real Estate'})
  WITH c
  MATCH (p:Person)-[:WORKS_IN]->(c)
  WITH p
  MATCH (p)-[:LIVES_IN]->(cou:Country)
  RETURN cou.name AS country, COUNT(p) AS count
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 3

question: List the top 2 countries where workers who speak Spanish live

question: Find the top 5 workers who work in companies that are located in the Hospitals and Health Care industry
cypher:
MATCH (w:Person)-[:WORKS_IN]->(:Company)-[:IS_IN]->(:Industry {name: 'Hospitals and Health Care'})
WITH w, COUNT(DISTINCT w) AS company_count
RETURN w.name AS worker_name, company_count
ORDER BY company_count DESC
LIMIT 5

question: What are the distinct countries that workers who speak Spanish live in? Top 5 results
cypher: MATCH (n:Person)-[:SPEAKS]->(:Language {name: 'Spanish'}), (n)-[:LIVES_IN]->(m:Country) RETURN DISTINCT m.name ORDER BY m.name LIMIT 5

question: List the companies that 'Haris Nadeem' has worked in. Show first 3 results
cypher: MATCH (p:Person {name: 'Haris Nadeem'})-[:WORKS_IN]->(c:Company) RETURN c LIMIT 3

question: How many workers who graduated from Centennial College live in Canada? Display first 3 results
cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:LIVES_IN]->(:Country {name: 'Canada'}) MATCH (p)-[:EDUCATED_AT]->(:School {name: 'Centennial College'}) RETURN p LIMIT 3

question: What are the top 5 industries that workers who graduated from California College of the Arts are associated with
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[:EDUCATED_AT]->(:School {name: 'California College of the Arts'})-[:WORKS_IN]->(c:Company)-[:IS_IN]->(i:Industry)
RETURN i.name, COUNT(*) as count
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 5

question: List the top 3 countries where workers named 'Paul Lukes' live
cypher: MATCH (p:Person {name: 'Paul Lukes'})-[:LIVES_IN]->(c:Country) RETURN c.name LIMIT 3

question: List the companies that are in the Advertising Services industry. First 3 results
cypher: MATCH (c:Company)-[:IS_IN]->(:Industry {name: 'Advertising Services'}) RETURN c.name LIMIT 3

question: Which workers are associated with the most number of companies? Display first 3 results
cypher:
MATCH (n:Person)-[r:WORKS_IN]->(m:Company)
        RETURN n.name, COLLECT(m.name) AS company_names, COUNT(*) as num_companies
        ORDER BY num_companies DESC
 LIMIT 3

question: What are the top 3 countries where workers from Search Engine People live
cypher: MATCH (c:Company {name: 'Search Engine People'}) <-[:WORKS_IN]-(p:Person)-[:LIVES_IN]->(cnt:Country) RETURN cnt.name, COUNT(cnt) ORDER BY COUNT(cnt) DESC LIMIT 3

question: Which person has worked in the most number of companies? First 3 results
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[r:WORKS_IN]->(c:Company)
RETURN p.name, collect(c.name) as companies
ORDER BY size(companies) DESC
LIMIT 3

question: List the workers who speak English and live in the United States. Display first 5 results
cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:SPEAKS]->(l:Language {name: 'English'}), (p)-[:LIVES_IN]->(c:Country {name: 'United States'}) RETURN p LIMIT 5

question: List the companies that workers who speak French are associated with. Show top 3 results
cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:SPEAKS]->(:Language {name: 'French'}), (p)-[:WORKS_IN]->(c:Company) RETURN DISTINCT(c.name) LIMIT 3

question: What are the top 5 countries where workers who graduated from the University of Healthcare and Social Service live
cypher: MATCH (c:School {name: 'University of Healthcare and Social Service'})<-[:EDUCATED_AT]-(p:Person)-[:LIVES_IN]->(co:Country) RETURN co.name, COUNT(p) as cnt ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 5

question: How many workers from the University of Healthcare and Social Service live in Canada? First 3 results
cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:EDUCATED_AT]->(s:School {name: 'University of Healthcare and Social Service'})-[:LIVES_IN]->(c:Country {name: 'Canada'}) MATCH (p)-[:WORKS_IN]->(comp:Company) RETURN DISTINCT comp.name LIMIT 3

question: What are the top 5 countries where workers who graduated from Ruby College of Higher Education live
cypher:
MATCH (s:School {name: 'Ruby College of Higher Education'})
      <-[:EDUCATED_AT]-(p:Person)-[:LIVES_IN]->(co:Country)
      RETURN co.name AS countries, COUNT(p.name) AS count
      ORDER BY count DESC
      LIMIT 5

question: How many workers who graduated from California College of the Arts live in the United States? Show first 3 results
cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:EDUCATED_AT]->(:School {name: 'California College of the Arts'})-[:LIVES_IN]->(:Country {name: 'United States'}) RETURN p LIMIT 3

question: Which workers live in the countries where French is commonly spoken? First 3 countries
cypher: MATCH (n:Person)-[:LIVES_IN]->(c:Country)<-[:IS_COMMONLY_SPOKEN]-(l:Language {name: 'French'}) RETURN n.name, c.name LIMIT 3

question: What are the companies that the person named 'Mev Sime' has worked in? List the first 3 companies
cypher: MATCH (p:Person { name: 'Mev Sime' })-[:WORKS_IN]->(c:Company) RETURN c LIMIT 3
